title: Myanmar Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Myanmar increased 17.05 percent in June of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Myanmar averaged 9.16 percent from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 42.10 percent in April of 2007 and a record low of -6.30 percent in April of 2012. This page provides - Myanmar Food Inflation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Organization, Myanmar
